Package org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworkservices.omf.rest

Class TemplateRequestBody

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworkservices.omf.rest.MetadataSourceRequestBody
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworkservices.omf.rest.TemplateRequestBody
public class TemplateRequestBody extends MetadataSourceRequestBody
TemplateRequestBody provides a structure for passing the properties for a new metadata element that is to be created via a template.
